{"word":"G5495 - χείρ - cheír - khire - Hand","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χείρ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">cheír</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khire</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hand</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"கை, கரம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"the hand"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Perhaps from the base of <a href=\"#/G5494 - χειμών - cheimṓn - khi-mone'/5494\">G5494</a> in the sense of its congener the base of <a href=\"#/G5490 - χάσμα - chásma - khas'-mah/5490\">G5490</a> (through the idea of <i>hollowness</i> for grasping); the <i>hand</i> (literally or figuratively [<i>power</i>]; especially [by Hebraism] a <i>means</i> or <i>instrument</i>): - hand.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5495/5495\">G5495</a>, <a href=\"#/G5496/5496\">G5496</a>, <a href=\"#/G5497/5497\">G5497</a>, <a href=\"#/G5498/5498\">G5498</a>, <a href=\"#/G5499/5499\">G5499</a>, <a href=\"#/G5500/5500\">G5500</a>, <a href=\"#/G886/886\">G886</a>"}]}